Bingo Caller
------------

This app is Catalyst based (perl) and is designed to be a web based simple bingo machine, that would be used at a bingo evening.

Objective:

Set a game up (location, max_number_drawn value, assume lowest value will be 1)

Click to 'draw' a random number from the range 1 -> max_number_drawn (default is the standard 90).

Display that.

Button to press if someone calls house or line, which will bring up grid of previously called numbers, highlighting last number called.

Allow to restart game if house/line call was not correct, else with line, carry game on for the house, or freeze game, and allow new game to be started.

Show previous 4 plus current numbers drawn at the bottom of the screen, as game is progressing.